=== Example 020: Basic diff command ===
Using backticks to call diff:
2c2
< This is line two
---
> This is line two modified
4c4
< This is line four
---
> This is a new line

diff with unified format (-u):
--- test_diff1.txt	2026-04-07 14:57:05.728299800 +0000
+++ test_diff2.txt	2026-04-07 14:57:05.730300700 +0000
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
 This is line one
-This is line two
+This is line two modified
 This is line three
-This is line four
+This is a new line
 This is line five

diff with context (-c):
*** test_diff1.txt	Tue Apr  7 14:57:05 2026
--- test_diff2.txt	Tue Apr  7 14:57:05 2026
***************
*** 1,5 ****
  This is line one
! This is line two
  This is line three
! This is line four
  This is line five
--- 1,5 ----
  This is line one
! This is line two modified
  This is line three
! This is a new line
  This is line five

